510
00:46:38,840 --> 00:46:40,274
這是沃倫先生和沃倫太太
It's Mr. and Mrs. Warren.

511
00:46:40,880 --> 00:46:43,554
我們現在都睡在樓下
We're all sleeping down here now.

512
00:46:44,000 --> 00:46:46,754
孩子們有點安全感，也更暖和一些
The girls feel safer and it's warmer.

513
00:46:47,120 --> 00:46:50,636
我一直開著暖氣，但這房子就是冷得要命
I'm constantly turning up the heat,but the house is always freezing.

514
00:46:50,800 --> 00:46:52,712
爐子沒什麼問題
It's not a problem with the furnace.

515
00:46:52,880 --> 00:46:54,155
我是說，我找不出原因
I mean, not that I can find.

516
00:46:59,400 --> 00:47:03,155
前幾晚情況越來越糟糕了
It's gotten a lot worse the past few nights.

517
00:47:03,680 --> 00:47:09,039
有股難聞的味道，像爛肉一樣，滿屋子都是
There's this awful smell, like rotting meat.It moves around the house.

518
00:47:12,000 --> 00:47:13,070
呃…
Uh....

519
00:47:13,240 --> 00:47:14,435
什麼？怎麼了？
What? What is it?

520
00:47:15,160 --> 00:47:20,519
腐臭味有可能是某種惡魔活動徵兆
Well, rancid smells could indicate some type of demonic activity.

521
00:47:20,760 --> 00:47:21,830
噢，上帝啊
Oh, my God.

522
00:47:26,280 --> 00:47:28,556
這是為了防止晚上發出碰門聲
That's to keep those doors from banging at night.

523
00:47:28,720 --> 00:47:32,157
不然，整晚都會像這樣響個不停
Otherwise, it's like...All night long, just like that.

524
00:47:33,520 --> 00:47:35,637
每天都會發生？  - 是的
Does it come in threes?  - Yeah.

525
00:47:35,800 --> 00:47:36,950
天亮就停？
It stops at dawn?

526
00:47:37,560 --> 00:47:38,755
對
Uh-huh.

527
00:47:40,760 --> 00:47:44,037
有時這意味著對三聖的不敬
Well, sometimes it's meant as an insult to the Trinity:

528
00:47:44,200 --> 00:47:46,157
聖父、聖子、聖靈
The Father, the Son and the Holy Spirit.

529
00:47:47,880 --> 00:47:51,476
知道嗎，這是非常邪惡的東西，但我們有辦法…
You know, it's the damndest thing,but we also get all kinds of birds...

530
00:47:51,680 --> 00:47:54,639
…可以把它從這房子裏找出來消滅掉
...that will just fly against the side of the house and break their necks.

531
00:47:54,800 --> 00:47:56,439
是嗎？
Hm. Really?

532
00:47:56,640 --> 00:47:59,030
鍾都停在了凌晨3:07
And the clocks stop at 3:07 a.m.

533
00:47:59,200 --> 00:48:01,271
所有的？  - 每個都是
All of them?  - Every one.

534
00:48:04,600 --> 00:48:07,434
噢，這些原本都是掛在樓梯上的
Oh, we were hanging those along the stairs.

535
00:48:07,600 --> 00:48:11,879
有東西老是會把它們弄下來，所以就不掛回去了
Something just kept knocking them down,so we stopped hanging them up.

536
00:48:15,320 --> 00:48:17,596
我一直在說
That's what I was talking about.

537
00:48:17,920 --> 00:48:19,673
我們搬來的時候它就已經在了
It was here when we moved in.

538
00:48:19,840 --> 00:48:22,036
地下室裏還有很多東西
There's also a lot of stuff in the cellar.

539
00:48:25,120 --> 00:48:26,440
帶我去地下室看看
Show me the cellar.

540
00:48:38,560 --> 00:48:41,155
看看她都讓我幹了些什麼
Look what she made me do.

541
00:48:41,400 --> 00:48:43,790
發現什麼了嗎，親愛的？
You picking up anything in here, hon?

542
00:48:47,520 --> 00:48:50,274
這裏發生過很可怕的事情，艾德
Something awful happened here, Ed.

543
00:48:54,080 --> 00:48:57,312
這些淤青，是來這裏之後出現的嗎？
Those bruises, they from something that happened here?

544
00:48:57,480 --> 00:49:01,520
這是因為我身體缺鐵什麼的
Oh, it's some iron deficiency thing I have.

545
00:49:03,520 --> 00:49:07,070
發生了那麼多事，你們為什麼不搬走？
You know, with all that's been going on,why haven't you just moved out?

546
00:49:07,400 --> 00:49:09,357
不知道我們可以搬去哪
I don't know where we'd move to, you know?

547
00:49:09,520 --> 00:49:13,833
我們把所有錢都花在了這裏，還進行了很多整修
We got all our money tied up in this place and had a lot of repairs on top of that.

548
00:49:14,480 --> 00:49:18,474
我也不知道誰可以長期收留我們一家七口人
And I don't know anybody whose gonna take in a family of seven indefinitely.

549
00:49:18,680 --> 00:49:20,558
所以我們找到了你們
That's why we tracked you down.

550
00:49:21,040 --> 00:49:22,793
很榮幸你們能來找我們
We're glad you found us.

551
00:49:23,280 --> 00:49:25,590
好，開始吧
All right, let's get started.

552
00:49:27,720 --> 00:49:31,157
我叫艾德·沃倫，今天是1971年11月1日
My name is Ed Warren.It's November 1st, 1971.

553
00:49:31,360 --> 00:49:33,352
我現在跟卡洛琳·佩倫坐在一起…
I'm sitting here with Carolyn Perron...

554
00:49:33,520 --> 00:49:37,719
…她的家庭正經歷著靈異事件
...who, with her family, has been experiencing supernatural occurrences.

555
00:49:38,640 --> 00:49:40,120
好，開始吧
Okay, go ahead.

556
00:49:41,640 --> 00:49:43,040
從哪裏說起？
Where do I start?

557
00:49:43,600 --> 00:49:45,273
從初次異常現象開始
From the first occurrence.

558
00:49:46,320 --> 00:49:48,357
我覺得應該是那些鍾
I guess it was the clocks.

559
00:49:48,520 --> 00:49:50,477
爸爸媽媽跟我說你有個朋友
Mom and Dad tell me that you have a friend.

560
00:49:50,640 --> 00:49:52,871
他叫羅利，他也住在這裏
His name's Rory.He lives here too.

561
00:49:53,040 --> 00:49:54,872
嗯  - 但他一直很悲傷
Hmm.  - But he's always sad.

562
00:49:55,040 --> 00:49:56,076
為什麼？
Why is that?

563
00:49:56,240 --> 00:50:00,029
他不告訴我，可能有什麼不好的事情發生在他身上了
He won't tell me but I think something bad happened to him.

564
00:50:02,760 --> 00:50:04,991
可以讓我見見羅利嗎？
Do you mind if I try to see Rory?

565
00:51:36,080 --> 00:51:37,150
嗨
Hey.

566
00:51:47,920 --> 00:51:49,195
怎麼了？
What is it?

567
00:52:10,360 --> 00:52:14,479
我們是從銀行拍賣來的，所以不知道之前誰住在這裏
We bought it at auction from the bank, so,you know, we never knew who lived here.

568
00:52:19,160 --> 00:52:24,360
羅琳跟我都覺得你們的房子需要「清潔」一下
Well, Lorraine and I both feel that what your house needs is a cleansing.

569
00:52:25,640 --> 00:52:26,835
一場驅魔儀式
An exorcism.

570
00:52:28,440 --> 00:52:29,874
什麼，驅魔？
What, exorcism?

571
00:52:31,840 --> 00:52:34,799
我一直以為驅魔是僅針對人的
I thought that was something that you do to people.

572
00:52:35,000 --> 00:52:36,354
不，不一定的
No, not necessarily, no.

573
00:52:37,000 --> 00:52:38,320
我們得離開這裏
We have to get out of here.

574
00:52:38,480 --> 00:52:40,472
恐怕這於事無補
I'm afraid that's not gonna help.

575
00:52:42,520 --> 00:52:44,796
羅琳看到了一些…
Lorraine saw something, which--

576
00:52:44,960 --> 00:52:46,235
你說吧，親愛的
Go ahead, hon.

577
00:52:48,680 --> 00:52:52,037
我看到你們的房子裏有邪惡之物出沒
I've been seeing the dark entity that haunts your house...

578
00:52:52,200 --> 00:52:53,714
…外面也有
...and your land.

579
00:52:58,240 --> 00:53:01,756
第一次看到它是在走進你們家門的時候
I saw it first when I came through your door.

580
00:53:01,920 --> 00:53:04,116
它就靠在你背上
It was latched to your back.

581
00:53:06,480 --> 00:53:10,679
第二次是在走進客廳的時候，它跟女孩們在一起
And then I saw it again with the girls when we walked into the living room.

582
00:53:11,600 --> 00:53:13,876
無論你們去哪裏…
And it doesn't matter where you go...

583
00:53:14,080 --> 00:53:17,198
…這邪物會一直跟著你們
...this dark entity has latched itself to your family...

584
00:53:17,360 --> 00:53:18,874
…吸食你們
...and it's feeding off you.

585
00:53:21,960 --> 00:53:24,077
哪怕我們離開也一樣？
Even if we leave?

586
00:53:24,240 --> 00:53:26,914
有時候鬼纏身，就像是踩到了口香糖
Sometimes when you get haunted,it's like stepping on gum.

587
00:53:27,480 --> 00:53:29,358
會一直粘著你
You take it with you.

588
00:53:30,280 --> 00:53:33,512
我得說，你們這裏有很多幽靈…
Look, I gotta tell you,you have a lot of spirits in here...

589
00:53:33,680 --> 00:53:38,277
…但這個是我們最擔心的，因為它充滿了仇恨
...but this is the one that I'm most worried about, because it is so hateful.

590
00:53:39,040 --> 00:53:41,999
好吧，那我們該怎麼做？叫個牧師來嗎？
Okay, so what do we do?Can we call a priest?

591
00:53:42,160 --> 00:53:43,480
那麼簡單就好了
I wish it were that easy.

592
00:53:43,640 --> 00:53:47,634
驅魔是一種很古老的儀式，需要很多年的訓練
Performing an exorcism is an archaic procedure. Requires years of training.

593
00:53:48,520 --> 00:53:52,560
哪怕這樣，慘劇還是會時常發生
And even then,I have seen it go horribly wrong.

594
00:53:53,520 --> 00:53:57,230
但在這之前，首先要獲得教堂的授權
But before we even get that far,the church has to authorize it first.

595
00:53:57,400 --> 00:54:00,632
就是說我們要調查、收集證物及提供證據…
It means we gotta investigate,gather evidence and provide proof...

596
00:54:00,840 --> 00:54:02,320
…這才是難點
...and that's the hard part.

597
00:54:04,480 --> 00:54:06,199
孩子們受過洗禮嗎？
Have your children been baptized?

598
00:54:06,360 --> 00:54:10,673
不，沒有，我們不常去教堂
Uh, no, we never got around to that.We're not really a churchgoing family.

599
00:54:10,920 --> 00:54:14,516
或許應該重新考慮一下，我們的出現或許會讓事情更糟糕
Well, you may want to rethink that.Our presence here could make things worse.

600
00:54:14,680 --> 00:54:15,796
為什麼？
Why?

601
00:54:15,960 --> 00:54:17,314
因為我們是個威脅
Because we're a threat.

602
00:54:17,520 --> 00:54:20,399
這裏這傢伙不太會喜歡我們
And whatever you're dealing with here isn't gonna like us.

603
00:54:20,560 --> 00:54:24,110
目前為止它還沒施過暴，這是個好現象
So far it hasn't done anything violent,and that's a good sign.

604
00:54:24,320 --> 00:54:27,199
所以我們會讓我們的人調查一下這裏…
So we're gonna have our guy do some homework on the property...

605
00:54:27,360 --> 00:54:29,158
…看看我們要對付的是什麼東西
...to see what we're up against.

606
00:54:31,400 --> 00:54:33,198
朱蒂，你要幹嗎？
Judy, what are you up to?

607
00:54:33,360 --> 00:54:36,114
我有禮物給你
I got you a present.

608
00:54:36,280 --> 00:54:39,352
我跟外婆在教堂的庭院市場上買的
Me and Nanna got these at the church's yard sale.

609
00:54:39,520 --> 00:54:41,352
寶貝  - 一個給你，一個給我
Honey.  - One for you and one for me.

610
00:54:41,520 --> 00:54:43,079
她在我這個裏…
She put a picture...

611
00:54:43,240 --> 00:54:44,515
…放了你和爸爸的照片
...of you and Daddy in mine.

612
00:54:45,040 --> 00:54:48,192
外婆說這樣我們就會永遠在一起
Nanna said this way we'll always be together.

613
00:54:48,360 --> 00:54:50,875
你我會一直在一起的
You'll be with me and I'll be with you.

614
00:54:53,560 --> 00:54:55,677
我想你和爸爸
I miss you and Daddy.

615
00:55:06,320 --> 00:55:07,436
嗨，親愛的
Hey, hon.

616
00:55:09,680 --> 00:55:10,716
在
Yup.

617
00:55:10,880 --> 00:55:13,714
你不會相信的，卡洛琳的聲音沒錄下來
You're not gonna believe this.Carolyn's voice didn't record.

618
00:55:15,080 --> 00:55:16,116
什麼意思？
What do you mean?

619
00:55:17,080 --> 00:55:18,275
聽著
Listen.

620
00:55:18,800 --> 00:55:22,237
我叫艾德·沃倫，今天是1971年11月1日
My name is Ed Warren.It's November 1st, 1971.

621
00:55:22,400 --> 00:55:24,232
現在跟卡洛琳·佩倫坐在一起…
I'm sitting here with Carolyn Perron...

622
00:55:24,400 --> 00:55:27,837
…她的家庭正經歷著靈異事件
...who, with her family, has been experiencing supernatural occurrences.

623
00:55:28,200 --> 00:55:29,554
好，開始吧
Okay, go ahead.

624
00:55:32,800 --> 00:55:34,598
從初次異常現象開始
From the first occurrence.

625
00:55:38,200 --> 00:55:39,475
什麼都沒有
Nothing.

626
00:55:40,080 --> 00:55:41,230
全程都是
The whole time.

627
