634
00:56:01,680 --> 00:56:03,592
被判了絞刑  - 哇噢
She was hung during the trials.  - Wow.

635
00:56:03,760 --> 00:56:06,639
巴斯希巴嫁給傑德森之後，生了個孩子…
After Bathsheba married Jedson,they had a baby...

636
00:56:06,840 --> 00:56:08,638
