So, what was the original 200-acre farm as since been subdivided and sold off.

649
00:56:47,920 --> 00:56:51,880
有個男孩在這個池塘裏淹死了，他住在這裏
There was another boy who drowned in pond here. He lived in a house over here.

650
00:56:52,040 --> 00:56:56,159
還有一個在附近做傭人的女人，也自殺了
And a woman who worked as a maid in a eighboring home, she committed suicide too.

651
00:56:58,080 --> 00:56:59,912
奪走她土地的人
People who took her land.

652
00:57:01,520 --> 00:57:03,796
現在跟卡洛琳·佩倫坐在一起…
I'm sitting here with Carolyn Perron...

653
00:57:03,960 --> 00:57:07,158
