Drew, this is Officer Brad.

659
00:57:59,160 --> 00:58:01,675
布拉德·漢密爾頓警官，羅德島哈瑞斯維爾警局的
Officer Brad Hamilton,Harrisville, Rhode Island P.D.

660
00:58:01,840 --> 00:58:03,718
